00:00:03.649 --> 00:00:07.359
How to Join an Online Digital Art Community.

00:00:07.359 --> 00:00:11.740
Start exploring and sharing your creative
side, or at least your love of digital art,

00:00:11.740 --> 00:00:14.849
with thousands of other online creators.

00:00:14.849 --> 00:00:22.570
You will need Username, password, and e-mail
address Account information Profile Participation

00:00:22.570 --> 00:00:25.830
and art uploads.

00:00:25.830 --> 00:00:26.900
Step 1.

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:30.179
Search the internet for an online art community
that suits you.

00:00:30.179 --> 00:00:34.650
There are websites with large groups, like
DeviantART, or smaller ones, for specialties

00:00:34.650 --> 00:00:36.950
such as graffiti art.

00:00:36.950 --> 00:00:37.950
Step 2.

00:00:37.950 --> 00:00:42.520
Choose a username and password for your account,
and enter any other required information,

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:44.120
such as your e-mail address.

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:48.890
Many online digital art communities allow
you to join and participate for free, but

00:00:48.890 --> 00:00:51.040
some charge a fee for services.

00:00:51.040 --> 00:00:55.030
Read the fine print and be sure you understand
the terms and conditions before submitting

00:00:55.030 --> 00:00:57.990
financial information.

00:00:57.990 --> 00:00:59.390
Step 3.

00:00:59.390 --> 00:01:00.620
Create your account.

00:01:00.620 --> 00:01:04.110
Some sites may require you to verify your
e-mail address before you can access their

00:01:04.110 --> 00:01:07.640
content and upload your own content.

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:08.980
Step 4.

00:01:08.980 --> 00:01:12.560
Explore the wealth of content available in
the online digital art community.

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:17.440
As you do, think about the kind of presence
you want to have on the site.

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:18.790
Step 5.

00:01:18.790 --> 00:01:22.870
Create an appealing profile that describes
and represents your interests and art-related

00:01:22.870 --> 00:01:24.930
activities.

00:01:24.930 --> 00:01:26.600
Step 6.

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:30.390
Participate in as many aspects of the online
community as you want, from commenting in

00:01:30.390 --> 00:01:34.640
discussion forums to buying original digital
art pieces.

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:38.970
Familiarize yourself with the rules of the
online community regarding inappropriate content,

00:01:38.970 --> 00:01:42.880
and be respectful in your comments on others'
work.

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:44.270
Step 7.

00:01:44.270 --> 00:01:48.440
Upload your own digital art creations to gain
exposure and constructive critiques of your

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:49.440
work.

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:53.100
The more you contribute, the more the online
art community grows.

00:01:53.100 --> 00:01:58.870
Did you know Photoshop, a popular photo and
digital editing software application, turned

00:01:58.870 --> 00:02:01.920
20 years old in February 2010.

